config BR2_PACKAGE_GATEWAYD
	bool "Wyze Sense Hub CC1310 radio daemon (gatewayd)"
	help
	  CC1310 sub-1GHz radio daemon for Wyze Sense Hub GW3U.
	  Reads sensor data from CC1310 via UART and publishes
	  to MQTT on localhost (gateways/# topics with HA auto-discovery).
	  Requires mosquitto (included in core config).
